comments: Westbrook (LAL) engage in incidental arm contact with Sengun (HOU) as they both pursue the rebound.
Sengun (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Reaves (LAL) firms up and absorbs the contact.
James (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position and cleanly blocks the driving shot attempt by Sengun (HOU).
HOU does not get a shot attempt off that makes contact with the rime, within the twenty four seconds allotted to them.
Martin Jr. (HOU) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Reaves (LAL), but extends his lower body into Reaves and affects his ability to defend around the pick.
Westbrook (LAL) extends his arm and makes contact with Green's (HOU) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Sengun (HOU) makes contact with the ball last before it goes OOB. LAL correctly maintain possession of the ball.
Gordon (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position during the running fade away shot attempt by James (LAL).
Replay confirmed that, Green (HOU) is last to make contact with the ball before it goes OOB. LAL correctly maintains possession of the ball.
As Westbrook (LAL) and Green (HOU) both meet in the paint, Westbrook does not extend his off arm into Green's body to dislodge him from his legal guarding position.
Martin Jr (HOU) makes marginal contact to Anthony's (LAL) body as he is in his upward shooting motion during the jump shot attempt.
